Package: ncmR
Type: Package
Title: Fit Neutral Community Model to Microbiome or Ecological Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Yuxuan", "He", , "heyuxuan0525@outlook.com", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0007-1149-5554"))
  )
Description: Provides tools for fitting the neutral community model (NCM) to 
    assess the role of stochastic processes in community assembly. The package 
    implements the framework of Sloan et al. (2006), enabling users to evaluate 
    neutral dynamics in ecological and microbial communities.
